biz.sudden.designCoordination.teamFormation.bottomUp.noticeboardAlgorithm
Class DeclaredCapability

java.lang.Object
  biz.sudden.designCoordination.teamFormation.bottomUp.noticeboardAlgorithm.DeclaredCapability

public class DeclaredCapability
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains the information within a declared capability - as serialised to AbsConcepts and back again. Further it provides a function to calculate the Matched capability resulting from applying this declared capability to a given potential extension.
